<li id="cite_note-15"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Joseph Smith, <a href="/wiki/Joseph_Fielding_Smith" title="Joseph Fielding Smith">Joseph Fielding Smith</a> (ed.) (1977). <i><a href="/wiki/Teachings_of_the_Prophet_Joseph_Smith_(book)" title="Teachings of the Prophet Joseph Smith (book)">Teachings of the Prophet Joseph Smith</a></i> (Salt Lake City, Utah: Deseret Book), p. 361.; italics in original.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/pgp/abr/3.18?lang=eng">Abraham 3:18</a>.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-17"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Boyd._K._Packer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Boyd. K. Packer (page does not exist)">Boyd. K. Packer</a>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/ensign/1995/11/the-brilliant-morning-of-forgiveness?lang=eng">"The Brilliant Morning of Forgiveness"</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/Ensign_(LDS_magazine)" title="Ensign (LDS magazine)">Ensign</a></i>, November 1995.</span>
